CrossingReality
Class SensorIgnoreIdTypeObject

java.lang.Object
  CrossingReality.SensorIgnoreIdTypeObject

public class SensorIgnoreIdTypeObject
extends java.lang.Object

Provides the representation of a sensor object for use by the 'prevent auto add this session' functionality of the Control Panel with regards to a sensor that has been removed from the Control Panel. Sensors are unique by combination of type & node id, so to store a reference to which sensor it is, we need to store which node id it is on and the type string.
